      "text": "Indexed\n44\n23\n\n+, having done this, the Spirit then transfers the rest of the Kerygma openly + fully. I did not realize how much had been revealed to me until that day -very recently- when I read the E.B. macro article on Messianic movements. Now I add to that the notion that Valis acted to transfer this knowledge to me in accretion upon accretion over a period of decades so that in 2-74 I did not just know the totality; I experienced it. To quote from \"Valis\": \"Reincarnation has nothing to do w",
